'''朱宇飆'''（{{bd|1971年|10月21日|catIdx=朱}}）[[中华人民共和国|中国]][[維權律师|維權律师]]，[[中山大學|中山大學]]法學碩士，[[廣東省|廣東省]]第一位幫[[法轮功|法轮功]]学员无罪辩护的律師，因此遭當局[[勞教|勞教]]、[[判刑|判刑]]、[[非法拘禁|非法拘禁]]及[[酷刑|酷刑]]，兩度被列入[[美國國務院|美國國務院]]2012、2013年度國際[[宗教自由|宗教自由]]報告<ref>{{cite news|title=2012 Report on International Religious Freedom|url=http://www.state.gov/j/drl/rls/irf/2012/eap/208222.htm|publisher=BUREAU OF DEMOCRACY, HUMAN RIGHTS, AND LABOR（美國國務院下屬機構）|quote=In July 2011 Guangzhou’s Haizhu District People’s Court sentenced lawyer Zhu Yubiao to two years’ imprisonment for possessing Falun Gong books and DVDs, according to online reporting. Zhu, who previously handled Falun Gong cases, had been held in police custody since August 2010 on charges of “using a cult to undermine the law.” Although Zhu was scheduled to be released in August, authorities transferred him to Sanshui Law School, where Falun Gong practitioners reportedly attend mandatory study sessions.|date=2013-05-20|language=en|accessdate=2015-06-19|archive-date=2017-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171125123100/https://www.state.gov/j/drl/rls/irf/2012/eap/208222.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=2013 Report on International Religious Freedom: China|url=http://www.state.gov/j/drl/rls/irf/2013/eap/222123.htm|publisher=BUREAU OF DEMOCRACY, HUMAN RIGHTS, AND LABOR（美國國務院機構）|date=2014-07-28|language=en|quote=([http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2014/07/29/a1126373.html 中文編譯報導])
Although Zhu Yubiao, a lawyer who had represented Falun Gong and under arrest since August 2010, was scheduled to be released in August 2012, authorities instead transferred him to Sanshui Law School in Foshan, Guangdong Province, where Falun Gong practitioners are reportedly forced to attend mandatory study sessions. Family members said Zhu began a hunger strike August 20, 2012 to protest his ongoing detention. No new information was available by year’s end.|accessdate=2015-06-19|archive-date=2019-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190510134357/https://www.state.gov/j/drl/rls/irf/2013/eap/222123.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他經常代理敏感案件而遭當局打壓，為底層群體辯護時經常低價、折價或義務免費，中國報紙曾兩次報導其事蹟。<ref name=hk2013/>

==生平==
2007年因為幫法輪功無罪辯護，被[[公安|公安]]以「反革命」理由抓捕並處一年半[[劳教|劳教]]並遭[[酷刑|酷刑]]，獲釋後當局曾嘗試无理要求其写下保证书不再维权作为發放律師證的交换条件<ref>{{cite news|author1=林静|title=被吊销执照的维权律师坚持行政诉讼|url=http://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/China_lawyer-09102010115635.html|agency=自由亞洲電台|date=2010-09-10|accessdate=2015-06-19|archive-date=2019-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191201163709/https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/China_lawyer-09102010115635.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他於2010年[[广州亚运会|广州亚运会]]前夕因為家中被當局抓捕並判刑2年，[[唐荆陵|唐荆陵]]指與幫法輪功辯護有關，家屬強烈抗議指當局政治迫害<ref>{{cite news|author1=丁小|title=RFA独家：法轮功律师朱宇飙 “预备犯罪”判两年|url=http://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/fa-07212011143205.html|agency=[[自由亞洲電台|自由亞洲電台]]|date=2011-07-21|accessdate=2015-06-19|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120233625/https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/fa-07212011143205.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=朱宇飆生平|url=http://www.64wiki.com/info/content.php?pid=1672|publisher=廣場活碑|access-date=2015-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619175807/http://www.64wiki.com/info/content.php?pid=1672|archive-date=2015-06-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author1=文宇晴|title=代理法輪功案件維權律師被判刑|url=http://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/china_lawyer-07222011102106.html/story_main?encoding=traditional|agency=自由亞洲電台|date=2011-07-22|accessdate=2015-06-19|archive-date=2019-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191203144846/https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/china_lawyer-07222011102106.html/story_main?encoding=traditional|dead-url=no}}</ref>，出獄後又被當局秘密送往廣東省三水法制教育所關押，因絕食抗議數十日陷入生命危險<ref name=hk2013>{{cite news|title=被酷刑对待的中国维权律师个案|url=http://www.chrlawyers.hk/zh-hans/content/被酷刑对待的中国维权律师个案|publisher=香港[[中国维权律师关注组|中国维权律师关注组]]|date=2013-06-26|accessdate=2021-12-27|archive-date=2019-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190828062145/http://www.chrlawyers.hk/zh-hans/content/%E8%A2%AB%E9%85%B7%E5%88%91%E5%AF%B9%E5%BE%85%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%BB%B4%E6%9D%83%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%88%E4%B8%AA%E6%A1%88|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Zhu Yubiao|publisher=[http://www.lawyersforlawyers.nl Lawyers for Lawyers]（營救各國受打壓律師的組織）|language=en}}</ref>。

